what our specific teaching

00:13:09.590 --> 00:13:13.430
goals were early in the teaching
encounter, or in a curriculum,

00:13:13.430 --> 00:13:17.480
and then doing some sort
of detection or assessment

00:13:17.480 --> 00:13:20.330
to determine how those goals
align with learners' objectives

00:13:20.330 --> 00:13:21.529
is important.

00:13:21.529 --> 00:13:23.570
Particularly in this
contemporary era in which we

00:13:23.570 --> 00:13:25.910
