student evaluations

00:13:25.910 --> 00:13:28.850
and their perceptions of
the utility of the courses

00:13:28.850 --> 00:13:31.447
and content that we develop.

00:13:31.447 --> 00:13:33.530
Along those lines, we
struggled with the challenge

00:13:33.530 --> 00:13:35.530
