different levels of knowledge,

00:13:38.780 --> 00:13:41.580
with different perspectives,
with different agendas

00:13:41.580 --> 00:13:45.160
coming into a teaching encounter
or into a course of curriculum.

00:13:45.160 --> 00:13:47.730
