Similarly, we
struggled with the idea

00:13:52.710 --> 00:13:55.770
of developing goals or
end-learning objectives that

00:13:55.770 --> 00:13:58.710
are more content
or factual based,

00:13:58.710 --> 00:14:02.640
and maybe less about analysis
and application and higher

00:14:02.640 --> 00:14:05.784
level skills, and how to
build those in a way that

00:14:05.784 --> 00:14:07.200
can be meaningful
for the learners

00:14:07.200 --> 00:14:09.840
and that can be assessed in a
meaningful way down the road.

