learning objectives,

00:14:34.980 --> 00:14:36.280
and assessment of learning.

00:14:36.280 --> 00:14:38.404
And so we had some really
interesting conversations

00:14:38.404 --> 00:14:41.255
about how to do that
because faculty will often

00:14:41.255 --> 00:14:43.380
think that everything
they're teaching is critical.

00:14:43.380 --> 00:14:45.390
