00:22:03.230 --> 00:22:04.910
or norms on the
part of the people

00:22:04.910 --> 00:22:07.100
learning in our different
situations, where

00:22:07.100 --> 00:22:09.620
they're actually
setting their own goals,

00:22:09.620 --> 00:22:10.730
or working towards that.

00:22:10.730 --> 00:22:13.550
And then we just help them
negotiate that with each other.

00:22:13.550 --> 00:22:16.820
We were also talking about
finding opportunities

00:22:16.820 --> 00:22:19.250
for more collaborative
activities where they can learn

00:22:19.250 --> 00:22:21.230
from each other,
rather than having

00:22:21.230 --> 00:22:22.880
us stand in as an instructor.

