finding opportunities for them

00:22:41.420 --> 00:22:45.350
to reflect or personalize
their approach

00:22:45.350 --> 00:22:49.970
to the content in a way that's
useful and applicable to them

00:22:49.970 --> 00:22:52.100
so that they know what
they're taking away

00:22:52.100 --> 00:22:55.170
while they're actually in
the learning situation.

00:22:55.170 --> 00:22:55.670
Great.

