of because it's going well

00:31:17.660 --> 00:31:20.600
for them, and one thing
they want to change.

00:31:20.600 --> 00:31:23.510
Which can come still
across as a complaint,

00:31:23.510 --> 00:31:26.360
but also it can come
as a more productive,

00:31:26.360 --> 00:31:27.620
constructive thought.

00:31:30.220 --> 00:31:30.940
Great.

00:31:30.940 --> 00:31:31.820
Wow.

